{"tid":1165030,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳情慾片流出　姚子羚強調係受害者","createTime":"2019-05-21T13:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T13:55:45.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9fba14e4499cb3f115e7e0fb8c59eba3e12e96","tid":1165030,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190521/photo/bkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001_01b.jpg?20190521131205\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20190521131205&h=a54e5d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫藝員姚子羚日前突爆出疑偷食夜店經理人夫Raymond，更一度傳出涉及四角戀，不過Raymond前妻蔡宛珊（Sarika）早於2017年已跟Raymond開始分居，今年初正式簽字離婚，證明姚子羚並非「第三者」。<br />\n<br />\n據知姚子羚早前提出分手，事有湊巧她與Raymond就流出床照，姚子羚覺得是有人刻意做出來，無非想影響她，對於盛傳兩人有情慾片流出，她斬釘截表示沒有跟Raymond影過任何情慾片，亦冇拍過AV，甚至冇赤裸與對方影過一張照片，她強調自己也是受害者。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190521/bkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190521%2Fbkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Td5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=519fae4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190521/bkn-20190521121608614-0521_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cdc87cfcbef90fd7970ef6ac584d53bc7bcf4630","tid":1165030,"uid":143033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}